---
import DocsLayout from "../../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout title="MinIO → OCI Object Storage - ITOps Automation Lab" activePage="minio-to-oci"
    lang="en"
    prev={{ label: "OCI Vault vs HashiCorp", href: "/en/aiops-lab/phase-9/oci-vault-vs-hashicorp" }}
    next={{ label: "Lab vs Production", href: "/en/aiops-lab/phase-9/lab-vs-prod" }}
>
    <div class="docs-page">
        <div class="h"><div class="h__top"><div class="h__badge">Phase 9.3</div><span class="h__time">Object Storage</span></div><h1 class="h__title">MinIO → OCI Object Storage<span class="h__accent"> · Storage Migration</span></h1><p class="h__sub">El mismo patron que Vault: en el lab local, MinIO como pod en k3s. En Oracle Cloud, OCI Object Storage como servicio gestionado. Loki usa la misma API S3 en ambos entornos — la migracion es transparente para los queries.</p></div>

        <div class="sec">
            <div class="sec__h"><span class="sec__num">01</span><h2 class="sec__h2">Comparacion</h2></div>
            <div class="cm"><div class="cm__lbl">Lab Local</div><div class="cm__title">MinIO (pod en k3s)</div><div class="cm__items"><span>Self-hosted, gestion manual</span><span>Almacenamiento en PVC de k3s</span><span>API S3-compatible</span><span>Ideal para desarrollo local</span></div></div>
            <div class="arr">↓</div>
            <div class="cm cm--oci"><div class="cm__lbl">Oracle Cloud</div><div class="cm__title">OCI Object Storage</div><div class="cm__items"><span>Managed, HA automatico</span><span>10 GB/mes gratis en Free Tier</span><span>API S3-compatible (misma interfaz)</span><span>Backend de Loki en produccion</span></div></div>
            <div class="info info--tip"><div class="info__icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg></div><div class="info__text"><b>Loki no cambia su configuracion.</b> Solo cambia el bloque storage_config del ConfigMap: de filesystem (lab local) a S3 con endpoint de OCI Object Storage. Los queries de LogQL, los dashboards de Grafana y los workflows de n8n funcionan exactamente igual.</div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="sec sec--cta">
            <div class="cta"><div class="cta__content"><h3 class="cta__title">Siguiente: Lab vs Production</h3><p class="cta__desc">Comparacion completa de los dos entornos: que cambia entre el lab local y Oracle Cloud.</p></div><a href="/en/aiops-lab/phase-9/lab-vs-prod" class="cta__btn"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21.5 2v6h-6M2.5 22v-6h6M2 11.5a10 10 0 0118.8-4.3M22 12.5a10 10 0 01-18.8 4.2"/></svg>Lab vs Prod</a></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</DocsLayout>

<style>
    .docs-page { max-width: 740px; }
    .h { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.875rem; padding: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .h__top { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .h__badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--green-300); padding: 0.35rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 0.4rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .h__time { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--text-dim); padding: 0.35rem 0.65rem; border-radius: 0.4rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
    .h__title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--green-50); line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .h__accent { color: var(--green-500); font-weight: 500; }
    .h__sub { font-size: var(--text-md); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 560px; }
    .sec { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .sec--cta { margin-top: 1rem; }
    .sec__h { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
    .sec__num { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--green-600); font-weight: 500; }
    .sec__h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-xl); font-weight: 600; color: var(--green-50); margin: 0; }
    .cm { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .cm--oci { border-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.1); background: rgba(59,130,246,0.02); }
    .cm__lbl { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-2xs); color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }
    .cm__title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-base); font-weight: 600; color: var(--green-50); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .cm__items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem; }
    .cm__items span { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.45; padding-left: 0.75rem; position: relative; }
    .cm__items span::before { content: "—"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--text-dim); }
    .arr { text-align: center; color: var(--green-500); font-size: var(--text-lg); padding: 0.25rem 0; font-weight: 700; }
    .info { display: flex; gap: 0.65rem; padding: 0.875rem 1rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.6rem; font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .info--tip { border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.2); background: rgba(34,197,94,0.03); }
    .info__icon { flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--green-400); margin-top: 0.1rem; }
    .info__icon svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; display: block; }
    .info__text b { color: var(--green-50); font-weight: 600; }
    .cta { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.75rem; }
    .cta__content { flex: 1; }
    .cta__title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-base); font-weight: 600; color: var(--green-50); margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
    .cta__desc { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.55; margin: 0; }
    .cta__btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: 500; color: var(--green-50); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 0.6rem 1rem; text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s; }
    .cta__btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-color: var(--border-hover); }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .cta { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; } }
</style>
